	  initialize floatin point values.

2006-09-09 Saturday 13:30  Roberto Bagnara <bagnara@cs.unipr.it>

	* src/LP_Problem.cc (1.18): Do not assume Coefficient is a GMP
	  integer.  Must include <cmath> for fabs().
