	* src/: Grid_Generator.defs.hh, Grid_Generator.inlines.hh,
	  Grid_conversion.cc, Grid_simplify.cc (grids.[23,18,35,46]): Move
	  negate(gg, start, end) to Grid_Generator::negate(start, end).

