	* src/: Checked_Number.inlines.hh, GMP_Integer.defs.hh,
	  GMP_Integer.inlines.hh (grids.[9,8,5]): Rename the wrapped
	  gcdext_assign function to gcdext_assign_r.  Take out the
	  four-parameter gcdext_assign function.

