2005-10-29 Saturday 09:53  Enea Zaffanella <zaffanella@cs.unipr.it>

	* src/: BD_Shape.defs.hh (1.38), BD_Shape.inlines.hh (1.72): In the
	  limited widening operators, we now avoid having to decode twice
