	* src/simplex.cc (1.5): Comment fixed.

2004-12-31 Friday 09:01  Roberto Bagnara <bagnara@cs.unipr.it>

	* src/simplex.cc (1.4): Variable-length automatic arrays are not
	  (yet) standard in C++: use vectors instead.

