	  interfaces/Prolog/XSB/expected_int64 (1.1),
	  interfaces/Prolog/XSB/expected_mpz (1.1),
	  interfaces/Prolog/YAP/Makefile.am (1.28): Another step toward the
	  generalization of the regression testing mechanisms.

