	  src/Polyhedra_Powerset.inlines.hh (1.3): The constructors
	  allowing to obtain a Polyhedra_Powerset<NNC_Polyhedron> from a
	  Polyhedra_Powerset<C_Polyhedron> and the other way around are now
	  explicit.

