	* src/SatRow.cc (1.15): Fixed int compare(const SatRow& x, const
	  SatRow& y), bool operator<=(const SatRow& x, const SatRow& y),
	  and bool operator<(const SatRow& x, const SatRow& y): they were
	  completely broken.

