2002-02-05 Tuesday 16:02  Elisa Ricci

	* src/Matrix.cc, src/Matrix.defs.hh, src/Polyhedron.cc,
	  src/Polyhedron.defs.hh, src/Polyhedron.inlines.hh, src/Row.cc,
	  src/Row.defs.hh, src/conversion.cc, src/minimize.cc,
