	* interfaces/Prolog/SICStus/solve.pl (1.18): Comments added
	  throughout.

2001-11-02 Friday 09:01  Elisa Ricci

	* src/Row.cc (1.10): In a comment of operator *(Row, Row) used
	  "dimension-compatible", instead of "dimension-compatibility".

